class="elementor-counter-number-wrapper"> <span class="elementor-counter-number-prefix"></span> <span class="elementor-counter-number" data-duration="2000" data-to-value="85" data-from-value="0" data-delimiter=",">0</span> <span class="elementor-counter-number-suffix">%</span> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a96d150 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="a96d150" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"> <div class="e-con-inner"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f3e7805 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="f3e7805" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-95be071 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="95be071" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b287532 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="b287532" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Your Mental Health Journey Is Unique.</h2> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-29308e1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="29308e1" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h4 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Your Treatment Plan Should Be Too.</h4> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-02cac96 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="02cac96" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <p>Resiliency Mind + Body Medicine is an integrative mental health clinic dedicated to promoting healthy lifestyle practices to help heal the mind and the body. Our clinic is physician-owned, meaning our practice focuses on the patient by providing the best treatment options for you and your health. The best part? We are<a title="Insurance" href="https://www.resiliencymbmedicine.com/insurance/"> in-network with most major insurances.</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-7fc8c0f elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="7fc8c0f" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <img width="300" height="163" alt="Resiliency Mind+Body Medicine - TMS for PTSD Newport Beach CA" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" nitro-lazy-srcset="https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Resiliency-MindBody-Medicine-Logo-300x163.png 300w, https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Resiliency-MindBody-Medicine-Logo.png 400w" nitro-lazy-src="https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Resiliency-MindBody-Medicine-Logo-300x163.png" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-4840 nitro-lazy" decoding="async" nitro-lazy-empty id="NjkwOjU2MA==-1" data-nitro-empty-id="NjkwOjU2MA==-1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMzAwIDE2MyIgd2lkdGg9IjMwMCIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxNjMiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PC9zdmc+" /> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-408e019 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="408e019" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-79a3311 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="79a3311" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-2afcdbe elementor-view-default elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon" data-id="2afcdbe" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="icon.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <div class="elementor-icon-wrapper"> <div class="elementor-icon"> <svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-check" viewbox="0 0 512 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M173.898 439.404l-166.4-166.4c-9.997-9.997-9.997-26.206 0-36.204l36.203-36.204c9.997-9.998 26.207-9.998 36.204 0L192 312.69 432.095 72.596c9.997-9.997 26.207-9.997 36.204 0l36.203 36.204c9.997 9.997 9.997 26.206 0 36.204l-294.4 294.401c-9.998 9.997-26.207 9.997-36.204-.001z"></path></svg> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-8cfc0af e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="8cfc0af" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f881137 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="f881137" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Integrative Psychiatry</h2> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-511ce41 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="511ce41" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <p>We provide physician-led, personalized care that combines advanced psychiatric treatment with integrative medicine to help patients build lasting resilience and whole-person wellness.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f1fd8bd e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="f1fd8bd" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-50e54cd elementor-view-default elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon" data-id="50e54cd" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="icon.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <div class="elementor-icon-wrapper"> <div class="elementor-icon"> <svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-check" viewbox="0 0 512 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M173.898 439.404l-166.4-166.4c-9.997-9.997-9.997-26.206 0-36.204l36.203-36.204c9.997-9.998 26.207-9.998 36.204 0L192 312.69 432.095 72.596c9.997-9.997 26.207-9.997 36.204 0l36.203 36.204c9.997 9.997 9.997 26.206 0 36.204l-294.4 294.401c-9.998 9.997-26.207 9.997-36.204-.001z"></path></svg> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ad9b702 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="ad9b702" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b335fee elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="b335fee" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Cutting-Edge Technology</h2> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5039f26 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="5039f26" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <p>At Resiliency Mind + Body Medicine, we offer advanced interventional psychiatry including BrainsWay® Deep TMS, Accelerated TMS (SWIFT protocol), SPRAVATO®, VNS therapy with the LivaNova Symmetry™ System, and NeuroLief ProLiV at home neuromodulation.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e25b5a0 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="e25b5a0" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-488be18 elementor-view-default elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon" data-id="488be18" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="icon.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <div class="elementor-icon-wrapper"> <div class="elementor-icon"> <svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-check" viewbox="0 0 512 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M173.898 439.404l-166.4-166.4c-9.997-9.997-9.997-26.206 0-36.204l36.203-36.204c9.997-9.998 26.207-9.998 36.204 0L192 312.69 432.095 72.596c9.997-9.997 26.207-9.997 36.204 0l36.203 36.204c9.997 9.997 9.997 26.206 0 36.204l-294.4 294.401c-9.998 9.997-26.207 9.997-36.204-.001z"></path></svg> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-8960bd5 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="8960bd5" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-24cab5a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="24cab5a" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">The Resiliency Difference</h2> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-4c030d6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="4c030d6" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <p>At Resiliency, mental health care is built around hope, healing, and progress. We strive to make every visit feel supportive, empowering, and grounded in a place where patients feel truly cared for.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-4f89da6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="4f89da6" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-aa970cb elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="aa970cb" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <div class="elementor-button-wrapper"> <a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="https://resiliencymbmedicine.com/new-patient-form/"> <span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper"> <span class="elementor-button-text">New Patient Inquiry</span> </span> </a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-4acf29f elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="4acf29f" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <div class="elementor-button-wrapper"> <a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="https://www.resiliencymbmedicine.com/contact/"> <span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper"> <span class="elementor-button-text">Book A Free Discovery Call</span> </span> </a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ccd4344 elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="ccd4344" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <div class="elementor-button-wrapper"> <a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="tel:9499965355"> <span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper"> <span class="elementor-button-icon"> <svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-mobile-alt" viewbox="0 0 320 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M272 0H48C21.5 0 0 21.5 0 48v416c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h224c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48V48c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48zM160 480c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32 32 14.3 32 32-14.3 32-32 32zm112-108c0 6.6-5.4 12-12 12H60c-6.6 0-12-5.4-12-12V60c0-6.6 5.4-12 12-12h200c6.6 0 12 5.4 12 12v312z"></path></svg> </span> <span class="elementor-button-text">Call Now</span> </span> </a> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d182fb0 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="d182fb0" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"> <div class="e-con-inner"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-07d0a57 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="07d0a57" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5c0dbb1 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="5c0dbb1" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-739b8db elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="739b8db" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Comprehensive Mental Health Services for Rapid Healing</h2> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-1e3e4b3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="1e3e4b3" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <p>Whether you are navigating mental health concerns, hormonal imbalances, or weight-related challenges, our experienced clinical team is here to help. We provide comprehensive evaluations and personalized treatment plans that may include medication management, Deep TMS, SPRAVATO® (esketamine) , hormone replacement therapy, and medically supervised weight loss options including GLP-1 medications to support whole-person healing and long-term wellness.</p> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ff8a51c elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="ff8a51c" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <div class="elementor-button-wrapper"> <a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="https://resiliencymbmedicine.com/contact/"> <span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper"> <span class="elementor-button-text">Learn More</span> </span> </a> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d2c926d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="d2c926d" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-df3248b elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="df3248b" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <img width="800" height="721" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" nitro-lazy-srcset="https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Resiliency01.jpg 800w, https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Resiliency01-300x270.jpg 300w, https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Resiliency01-768x692.jpg 768w" nitro-lazy-src="https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Resiliency01.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-14338 nitro-lazy" decoding="async" nitro-lazy-empty id="ODIxOjUzMQ==-1" data-nitro-empty-id="ODIxOjUzMQ==-1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDcyMSIgd2lkdGg9IjgwMCIgaGVpZ2h0PSI3MjEiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PC9zdmc+" /> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-37dd014 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="37dd014" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-745cf04 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="745cf04" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d6ecc6b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="d6ecc6b" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">BrainsWay® Deep TMS: A Breakthrough in Depression and PTSD Treatment</h2> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b64355b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="b64355b" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <p class="" data-start="1659" data-end="1865">Deep TMS uses magnetic pulses to stimulate underactive brain regions that regulate mood. It is safe, medication-free, and ideal for individuals who have not responded to traditional psychiatric treatment.</p><ul data-start="1867" data-end="2027"><li class="" data-start="1867" data-end="1896"><p class="" data-start="1869" data-end="1896">No anesthesia or downtime</p></li><li class="" data-start="1897" data-end="1932"><p class="" data-start="1899" data-end="1932">Covered by <a href="https://www.resiliencymbmedicine.com/insurance/">most insurance plans</a></p></li><li class="" data-start="1933" data-end="1971"><p class="" data-start="1935" data-end="1971">FDA-approved for depression, OCD, anxious depression, smoking cessation</p></li><li class="" data-start="1933" data-end="1971"><p class="" data-start="1935" data-end="1971">FDA-cleared for ages 15+</p></li><li class="" data-start="1972" data-end="2027"><p class="" data-start="1974" data-end="2027">Now used effectively for PTSD and anxiety disorders</p></li></ul><p class="" data-start="2029" data-end="2056">&nbsp;</p> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-891f299 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="891f299" data-element_type="c