on-list-item"> <span class="elementor-icon-list-icon"> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewbox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6.40038 18.3079L5.69238 17.5999L11.2924 11.9999L5.69238 6.39989L6.40038 5.69189L12.0004 11.2919L17.6004 5.69189L18.3084 6.39989L12.7084 11.9999L18.3084 17.5999L17.6004 18.3079L12.0004 12.7079L6.40038 18.3079Z" fill="black"></path></svg> </span> <span class="elementor-icon-list-text">Minimal Outcome Tracking</span> </li> <li class="elementor-icon-list-item"> <span class="elementor-icon-list-icon"> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewbox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6.40038 18.3079L5.69238 17.5999L11.2924 11.9999L5.69238 6.39989L6.40038 5.69189L12.0004 11.2919L17.6004 5.69189L18.3084 6.39989L12.7084 11.9999L18.3084 17.5999L17.6004 18.3079L12.0004 12.7079L6.40038 18.3079Z" fill="black"></path></svg> </span> <span class="elementor-icon-list-text">Unknown Provider Training and Experience</span> </li> <li class="elementor-icon-list-item"> <span class="elementor-icon-list-icon"> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewbox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6.40038 18.3079L5.69238 17.5999L11.2924 11.9999L5.69238 6.39989L6.40038 5.69189L12.0004 11.2919L17.6004 5.69189L18.3084 6.39989L12.7084 11.9999L18.3084 17.5999L17.6004 18.3079L12.0004 12.7079L6.40038 18.3079Z" fill="black"></path></svg> </span> <span class="elementor-icon-list-text">Single Location Only</span> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ed4fae6 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child" data-id="ed4fae6" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="e-con-inner"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3d47300 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="3d47300" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-32c23b3 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="32c23b3" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-4660558 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="4660558" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Finally Find the Right Option for You</h2> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d57d9f9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="d57d9f9" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> At Resiliency Mind + Body Medicine, we offer personalized treatment options to support your journey toward lasting relief and resiliency. Whether you’re exploring TMS for the first time or seeking advanced care, we have a plan that fits your needs. </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9e65651 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="9e65651" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-23cc277 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="23cc277" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;gradient&quot;}"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b57ed21 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="b57ed21" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Deep TMS Therapy</h3> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ccb87f5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="ccb87f5" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <p>FDA-approved, non-invasive treatment designed to target the brain areas linked to depression, anxiety, PTSD, and OCD.</p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-66754d1 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="66754d1" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;gradient&quot;}"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-53e7a5d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="53e7a5d" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Accelerated TMS Protocols</h3> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6046f2e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="6046f2e" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <p>Personalized TMS protocols on your schedule, tailored to your symptoms, goals, and treatment history.</p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-8c6324f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="8c6324f" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;gradient&quot;}"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9d33181 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="9d33181" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Interventional Care</h3> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-1dce0a5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="1dce0a5" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <p>We offer comprehensive interventional psychiatry options including BrainsWay® Deep TMS, SPRAVATO® (esketamine) and more to personalize treatment for complex, treatment-resistant conditions.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e10086b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="e10086b" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" id="services" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"> <div class="e-con-inner"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f847ce2 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="f847ce2" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-fc30fbc e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="fc30fbc" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-febe61f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="febe61f" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Our Services</h2> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a606ef4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="a606ef4" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <p>At Resiliency Mind + Body Medicine, we provide a comprehensive range of mental health treatments rooted in neuroscience, psychiatry, and integrative care. Whether you&#8217;re navigating treatment-resistant depression, anxiety, PTSD, or ADHD, our services are designed to address the root cause—not just the symptoms. With convenient locations in Newport Beach and San Juan Capistrano, our patients benefit from easier access to care, greater scheduling flexibility, and continuity of treatment close to home.</p> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a7a7e75 elementor-arrows-position-inside elementor-widget elementor-widget-n-carousel" data-id="a7a7e75" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-settings="{&quot;carousel_items&quot;:[{&quot;slide_title&quot;:&quot;Slide #1&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;d7258f8&quot;},{&quot;slide_title&quot;:&quot;Slide #2&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;3806be1&quot;},{&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;3cafaa1&quot;,&quot;slide_title&quot;:&quot;Slide #5&quot;},{&quot;slide_title&quot;:&quot;Sparvato&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;d7fe876&quot;},{&quot;slide_title&quot;:&quot;Slide #3&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;615e631&quot;},{&quot;slide_title&quot;:&quot;Slide #3&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;78021f6&quot;}],&quot;slides_to_show_tablet&quot;:&quot;2&quot;,&quot;slides_to_show_mobile&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;infinite&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;speed&quot;:500,&quot;offset_sides&quot;:&quot;none&quot;,&quot;arrows&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;image_spacing_custom&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:10,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;image_spacing_custom_tablet&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;image_spacing_custom_mobile&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]}}" data-widget_type="nested-carousel.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <div class="e-n-carousel swiper" role="region" aria-roledescription="carousel" aria-label="Carousel" dir="ltr"> <div class="swiper-wrapper" aria-live="polite"> <div class="swiper-slide" data-slide="1" role="group" aria-roledescription="slide" aria-label="1 of 6"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-091d277 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child" data-id="091d277" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="e-con-inner"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f837d92 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="f837d92" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-24c89ae elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="24c89ae" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <img width="800" height="420" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" nitro-lazy-srcset="https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/What-is-Transcranial-Magnetic-Stimulation-TMS_--1024x538.jpg 1024w, https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/What-is-Transcranial-Magnetic-Stimulation-TMS_--300x158.jpg 300w, https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/What-is-Transcranial-Magnetic-Stimulation-TMS_--768x403.jpg 768w, https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/What-is-Transcranial-Magnetic-Stimulation-TMS_-.jpg 1200w" nitro-lazy-src="https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/What-is-Transcranial-Magnetic-Stimulation-TMS_--1024x538.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-7893 nitro-lazy" decoding="async" nitro-lazy-empty id="MTA2Nzo4MTA=-1" data-nitro-empty-id="MTA2Nzo4MTA=-1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMTAyNCA1MzgiIHdpZHRoPSIxMDI0IiBoZWlnaHQ9IjUzOCIgeG1sbnM9Imh0dHA6Ly93d3cudzMub3JnLzIwMDAvc3ZnIj48L3N2Zz4=" /> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6d1de01 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="6d1de01" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-72f15a4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="72f15a4" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h4 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><a href="https://www.resiliencymbmedicine.com/tms-newportbeach/">Deep TMS Therapy</a></h4> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-fd718d7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="fd718d7" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <p>We specialize in Deep Transcranial Magnetic Stimulation (TMS)—a non-invasive, FDA-cleared treatment for major depressive disorder, OCD, and PTSD. This outpatient therapy uses magnetic pulses to stimulate underactive areas of the brain associated with mood regulation. Deep TMS is safe, well-tolerated, and ideal for individuals who have not responded to medication or therapy alone. Most major insurance plans cover TMS therapy.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="swiper-slide" data-slide="2" role="group" aria-roledescription="slide" aria-label="2 of 6"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f2cc5cb e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child" data-id="f2cc5cb" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="e-con-inner"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3099d78 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="3099d78" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-24f9c0e elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="24f9c0e" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <img width="768" height="768" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px" nitro-lazy-srcset="https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/spravato-28mg-768x768.png 768w, https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/spravato-28mg-300x300.png 300w, https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/spravato-28mg-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/spravato-28mg-150x150.png 150w, https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/spravato-28mg.png 1080w" nitro-lazy-src="https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/spravato-28mg-768x768.png" class="attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-12823 nitro-lazy" decoding="async" nitro-lazy-empty id="MTA4OTo3NDc=-1" data-nitro-empty-id="MTA4OTo3NDc=-1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNzY4IDc2OCIgd2lkdGg9Ijc2OCIgaGVpZ2h0PSI3NjgiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PC9zdmc+" /> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ed3f08d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="ed3f08d" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-8de1433 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="8de1433" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h4 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">SPRAVATO®</h4> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-612f139 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="612f139" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-2" data-scroll-anchor="true"><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[72rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" dir="auto" data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="cf1d7020-d065-40c5-b284-c67ef537ef33" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="382" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">SPRAVATO® (esketamine) is an FDA-approved nasal spray used alongside an oral antidepressant to treat adults with treatment-resistant depression or major depressive disorder with suicidal thoughts. SPRAVATO® works differently from traditional antidepressants by targeting the brain&#8217;s glutamate system to relieve symptoms more rapidly.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><div class="pointer-events-none h-px w-px" aria-hidden="true" data-edge="true">&nbsp;</div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="swiper-slide" data-slide="3" role="group" aria-roledescription="slide" aria-label="3 of 6"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-fd3208c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child" data-id="fd3208c" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="e-con-inner"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-fa7b32e e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="fa7b32e" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d75f46d elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="d75f46d" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <img width="768" height="786" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px" nitro-lazy-srcset="https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/What-is-Ketamine-Therapy-768x786.webp 768w, https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/What-is-Ketamine-Therapy-293x300.webp 293w, https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/What-is-Ketamine-Therapy.webp 1000w" nitro-lazy-src="https://cdn-ildmphd.nitrocdn.com/tzzcgexpyBvSGkQdyIokdkbspoHSRNJM/assets/images/optimized/rev-580c2f1/resiliencymbmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/What-is-Ketamine-Therapy-768x786.webp" class="attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8351 nitro-lazy" decoding="async" nitro-lazy-empty id="MTExMTo2MDc=-1" data-nitro-empty-id="MTExMTo2MDc=-1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNzY4IDc4NiIgd2lkdGg9Ijc2OCIgaGVpZ2h0PSI3ODYiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PC9zdmc+" /> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ea843db e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="ea843db" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d0d32df elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="d0d32df" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h4 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><a href="http://Medication%20Management">Medication Management</a></h4> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-1afa8e3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="1afa8e3" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <p>Our providers offer thoughtful, root-cause-focused medication management, rather than one-size-fits-all prescribing. We monitor efficacy and side effects closely, making data-informed adjustments to optimize your results. Whether you’re starting psychiatric medication for the first time or reevaluating your current regimen, we’re here to help you find what works best for you.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="swiper-slide" data-slide="4" role="group" aria-roledescription="slide" aria-label="4 of 6"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a0b79c3 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child" data-id="a0b79c3" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="e-con-inner"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-78f8776 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="78f8776" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-2a061be elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="2a061be" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <a href="https://www.neurohealthmd.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> <img width="768" height="1