-heading" data-id="0b70411" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Stefani LaFrenierre, MD</h2> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-2e7921d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="2e7921d" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h4 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Founder/Chief Medical Officer</h4> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-8e3b32e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="8e3b32e" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <p>Our team is led by Dr. Stefani LaFrenierre, MD, a double-board certified psychiatrist with a passion for integrative, evidence-based care. With extensive experience in treating complex mood disorders, trauma, and psychosis, Dr. LaFrenierre brings a comprehensive and compassionate approach to mental health. She leads a multidisciplinary team of psychiatrists, psychiatric nurse practitioners, physician associates, and psychiatry technicians who share her commitment to personalized treatment, clinical excellence, and whole-person healing. Under her leadership, Resiliency Mind+Body Medicine offers a collaborative environment where patients receive thoughtful, individualized care that addresses both the biological and lifestyle factors impacting their mental health.</p> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d3f7525 elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="d3f7525" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <div class="elementor-button-wrapper"> <a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="https://resiliencymbmedicine.com/contact/"> <span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper"> <span class="elementor-button-text">Contact Us </span> </span> </a> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b527646 elementor-hidden-desktop elementor-hidden-tablet elementor-hidden-mobile e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="b527646" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"> <div class="e-con-inner"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-534fc46 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="534fc46" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-0a6c6fd e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="0a6c6fd" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5ee89c0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="5ee89c0" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><a href="https://www.resiliencymbmedicine.com/our-team/">Our Team</a></h2> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-95c3196 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="95c3196" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <p>Our team is led by Dr. Stefani LaFrenierre, MD, a board-certified psychiatrist with a passion for integrative, evidence-based care. With extensive experience in treating complex mood disorders, trauma, and anxiety, Dr. LaFrenierre brings a comprehensive and compassionate approach to mental health. She leads a multidisciplinary team of psychiatric nurse practitioners, physician associates, and wellness specialists who share her commitment to personalized treatment, clinical excellence, and whole-person healing. Under her leadership, Resiliency Mind + Body Medicine offers a collaborative environment where patients receive thoughtful, individualized care that addresses both the biological and lifestyle factors impacting their mental health.</p> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-31b417a elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="31b417a" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <div class="elementor-button-wrapper"> <a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="https://www.resiliencymbmedicine.com/our-team/"> <span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper"> <span class="elementor-button-text">Learn More</span> </span> </a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-bbfcae2 elementor-pagination-type-bullets elementor-arrows-position-inside elementor-pagination-position-outside elementor-widget elementor-widget-n-carousel" data-id="bbfcae2" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-settings="{&quot;carousel_items&quot;:[{&quot;slide_title&quot;:&quot;Dr. Stefani LaFrenierre, MD&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;d7258f8&quot;},{&quot;slide_title&quot;:&quot;Dr. Erin Griffiths, DO, MA&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;df3178c&quot;},{&quot;slide_title&quot;:&quot;Dr. Heather Wong, DMSc, MPAS, PA-C, CAQ-Psych&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;3806be1&quot;},{&quot;slide_title&quot;:&quot;Milinda Estrada&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;67462c4&quot;},{&quot;slide_title&quot;:&quot;Regina Dizon, PMHNP-BC&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;78021f6&quot;},{&quot;slide_title&quot;:&quot;Brian Tran, PMHNP\u2011BC&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;29a440b&quot;},{&quot;slide_title&quot;:&quot;Lina Kurdi, PMHNP-BC&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;b4a7a0f&quot;},{&quot;slide_title&quot;:&quot;Lauren Kim&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;29973e2&quot;},{&quot;slide_title&quot;:&quot;Jeffrey Phan&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;4dbcb