QABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-673f84e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="673f84e" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Yuli Plascencia</h3> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-1c5412b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="1c5412b" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <p>Revenue Cycle &amp; Operations Coordinator</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-swiper-button elementor-swiper-button-prev" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="Previous"> <svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-eicon-chevron-left" viewbox="0 0 1000 1000" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M646 125C629 125 613 133 604 142L308 442C296 454 292 471 292 487 292 504 296 521 308 533L604 854C617 867 629 875 646 875 663 875 679 871 692 858 704 846 713 829 713 812 713 796 708 779 692 767L438 487 692 225C700 217 708 204 708 187 708 171 704 154 692 142 675 129 663 125 646 125Z"></path></svg> </div> <div class="elementor-swiper-button elementor-swiper-button-next" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="Next"> <svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-eicon-chevron-right" viewbox="0 0 1000 1000" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M696 533C708 521 713 504 713 487 713 471 708 454 696 446L400 146C388 133 375 125 354 125 338 125 325 129 313 142 300 154 292 171 292 187 292 204 296 221 308 233L563 492 304 771C292 783 288 800 288 817 288 833 296 850 308 863 321 871 338 875 354 875 371 875 388 867 400 854L696 533Z"></path></svg> </div> <div class="swiper-pagination"></div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6816219 elementor-hidden-desktop elementor-hidden-tablet elementor-hidden-mobile e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="6816219" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="e-con-inner"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ffff9f9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="ffff9f9" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Frequently Asked Questions</h2> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6defb77 elementor-widget elementor-widget-n-accordion" data-id="6defb77" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-settings="{&quot;default_state&quot;:&quot;expanded&quot;,&quot;max_items_expended&quot;:&quot;one&quot;,&quot;n_accordion_animation_duration&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;ms&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:400,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]}}" data-widget_type="nested-accordion.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <div class="e-n-accordion" aria-label="Accordion. Open links with Enter or Space, close with Escape, and navigate with Arrow Keys"> <details id="e-n-accordion-item-1150" class="e-n-accordion-item" open> <summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="1" tabindex="0" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1150"> <span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> What makes Resiliency Mind + Body Medicine different from other mental health practices in Orange County? </div></span> <span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'> <span class='e-opened'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-minus" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></svg></span> <span class='e-closed'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-plus" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></svg></span> </span> </summary> <div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1150" class="elementor-element elementor-element-b497f99 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="b497f99" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-fff5832 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="fff5832" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> We combine traditional psychiatry with integrative modalities like functional medicine, IV nutrient therapy, and aesthetic wellness to address both biological and lifestyle factors affecting mental health. Our focus is on treating root causes, not simply managing symptoms. Also, being physician-owned, we can ensure treatment plans are tailored and high quality, with board-certified providers and flexible options (in-person or virtual). </div> </div> </div> </details> <details id="e-n-accordion-item-1151" class="e-n-accordion-item"> <summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="2" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1151"> <span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> Is TMS Deep Transcranial Magnetic Stimulation covered by insurance here in Newport Beach? </div></span> <span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'> <span class='e-opened'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-minus" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></svg></span> <span class='e-closed'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-plus" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></svg></span> </span> </summary> <div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1151" class="elementor-element elementor-element-853aef1 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="853aef1" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e99e70a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="e99e70a" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> Yes, Deep TMS is FDA-cleared and many of our patients have insurance that covers it for depression and OCD, and increasingly for PTSD and anxiety depending on the insurer. We handle insurance verification for you and help with prior authorizations as needed. It’s best to contact us with your insurance information for a precise answer. </div> </div> </div> </details> <details id="e-n-accordion-item-1152" class="e-n-accordion-item"> <summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="3" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1152"> <span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> Can I receive care virtually, or do I need to come to the office physically? </div></span> <span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'> <span class='e-opened'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-minus" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></svg></span> <span class='e-closed'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-plus" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></svg></span> </span> </summary> <div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1152" class="elementor-element elementor-element-d8a4faa e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="d8a4faa" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ccb360f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="ccb360f" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> We offer both in-person appointments at our Newport Beach and San Juan Capistrano locations, as well as virtual telemedicine options for many of our psychiatric and integrative services. Some treatments like TMS or Spravato require in-office visits due to equipment or supervision needs. During your initial consultation we’ll determine which parts of your care can be done remotely. </div> </div> </div> </details> <details id="e-n-accordion-item-1153" class="e-n-accordion-item"> <summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="4" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1153"> <span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> How do you personalize treatment plans for patients with mental health conditions? </div></span> <span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'> <span class='e-opened'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-minus" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></svg></span> <span class='e-closed'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-plus" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></svg></span> </span> </summary> <div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1153" class="elementor-element elementor-element-2ac475a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="2ac475a" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-dddcc66 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="dddcc66" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> Personalization starts with a thorough assessment including mental health history, prior treatment responses, medication history, lifestyle, medical labs, and functional medicine metrics. Then our team of psychiatrists, nurse practitioners, and wellness specialists collaborates to design a plan that may include TMS, medication, Spravato®, nutritional support, IV therapy, or lifestyle changes. We monitor closely and adjust as needed for optimal outcomes. </div> </div> </div> </details> <details id="e-n-accordion-item-1154" class="e-n-accordion-item"> <summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="5" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1154"> <span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> What kind of results can I expect, and how quickly will I feel better? </div></span> <span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'> <span class='e-opened'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-minus" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></svg></span> <span class='e-closed'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-plus" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z"></path></svg></span> </span> </summary> <div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1154" class="elementor-element elementor-element-a939188 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="a939188" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-793ecf6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="793ecf6" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> Results vary by condition, severity, and treatment chosen. For many patients, symptom relief begins within the first few weeks of TMS or Spravato®. Others may need more sessions before significant change. Long-term improvements in mood, anxiety, sleep, and function are often reported. Our aim is sustained improvement rather than only fast but temporary relief. </div> </div> </div> </details> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div data-id="6027141" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}" class="elementor-element elementor-element-6027141 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent nitro-lazy"> <div class="e-con-inner"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-7e16c38 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="7e16c38" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-bcc3ccb e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child" data-id="bcc3ccb" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="e-con-inner"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d64c90f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="d64c90f" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Schedule a Consultation</h2> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-4fc01fb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="4fc01fb" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> Ready to take the next step? Schedule a consultation today to learn more about how we can help you achieve your health and wellness goals. Our team is here to provide you with the information you need to make informed decisions about your care. </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a7cd7dd e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="a7cd7dd" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container"> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-7530680 elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="7530680" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <div class="elementor-button-wrapper"> <a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="https://resiliencymbmedicine.com/new-patient-form/" target="_blank" title="Intake Form"> <span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper"> <span class="elementor-button-text">New Patient Inquiry</span> </span> </a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6ba8f83 elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="6ba8f83" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <div class="elementor-button-wrapper"> <a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="https://www.resiliencymbmedicine.com/contact/"> <span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper"> <span class="elementor-button-text">Book A Free Discovery Call</span> </span> </a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-89d41e8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="89d41e8" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default"> <div class="elementor-widget-container"> <div class="elementor-button-wrapper"> <a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="tel:9499965355"> <span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper"> <span class="elementor-button-icon"> <svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-mobile-alt" viewbox="0 0 320 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M272 0H48C21.5 0 0 21.5 0 48v416c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h224c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48V48c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48zM160 480c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32 32 14.3 32 32-14.3 32-32 32zm112-108c0 6.6-5.4 12-12 12H60c-6.6 0-12-5.4-12-12V60c0-6.6 5.4-12 12-12h200c6.6 0 12 5.4 12 12v312z"></path></svg> </span> <span class="elementor-button-text">Call Now</span> </span> </a> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <script nitro-exclude>
